tool_description: This API gives you access to tons on movies, ready for download for free
title: Latest Movies

api_list.name: Get All Movies
api_list.description: This endpoint will return all the latest movies available for download
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://latest-movies.p.rapidapi.com/movies"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "latest-movies.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
